data.description: A tranquil retreat perched above Shannopin Country Club! This sprawling ranch nestled in the heart of a quiet, desirable location offers an opportunity you wont want to miss. Meticulously maintained & updated by the current owners, this home boasts 3 spacious bedrooms, 2.5 baths, a massive living room, a large dining room & a fabulous game room that you may never want to leave. You will love the charming features still in tact such as original built-ins, two fireplaces, and the hardwood floors beneath the carpets. The bright and airy kitchen functions perfectly with ample storage. Step outside to the private screened-in porch to enjoy the wooded views with a cup of coffee. The 3 bedrooms located on the main floor include spacious closets and 2 full baths, one beautifully remodeled in 2022. The finished basement includes a huge sports bar, a lounge area, a newly added powder room and a laundry room.  Additional features include a two-car garage, bonus storage rooms, and a flat backyard.
